N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4627.19 - Stay without court order

State Regulations

The commission shall have discretion to stay all
proceedings to enforce any action, determination or order appealed from, upon
written application to the commission by the party aggrieved and for good cause
shown by affidavit of the moving party. Notes
